title: 1BR/1BTH for RENT. 13th Mo rent free w/12 Mo Lease
posting_body: ['Non-Smoking 1 BR/1 BTH units for rent in the Maplewood/North St Paul area.', ' Great location minutes from hwy 36 & Hwy 94.', 'Very quiet, clean, family friendly.', '13th month rent free with a 12-month lease!!!!', '*Heat, water and trash included in the rent.*', 'Amenities:', 'Control entrances', 'Outdoor pool', 'Onsite laundry', 'Parking Lot/street parking', 'Detached garages available', '$35.00 application fee per adults (anyone over the age of 18 yrs old).', 'Rent-$890.00', 'Deposit- $500.00', 'Minimum monthly income of $2,225.00', 'Cats welcomed with a deposit of $250.00/$100.00 Non-refundable and a monthly pet rent of $25.00.', 'If you have any questions or would like to schedule a showing, please contact the rental office at', 'show contact info', '.']
